    {
      "block_id": "b00013",
      "text": "(一)备案基本信息表;",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 499,
      "end_char": 510,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00014",
      "text": "(二)信用保护合约主协议;",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 512,
      "end_char": 525,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00015",
      "text": "(三)信用保护合约补充协议。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 527,
      "end_char": 541,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00016",
      "text": "第九条 协会对信用保护合约主协议及补充协议的备案进行齐备性审核,审核内容包括但不限于:",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 543,
      "end_char": 586,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00017",
      "text": "(一)备案材料是否齐备;",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 588,
      "end_char": 600,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00018",
      "text": "(二)主协议和补充协议要素是否完备。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 602,
      "end_char": 620,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00019",
      "text": "第十条 备案材料齐备的,协会在材料齐备后5个工作日内出具电子备案确认函。备案材料不齐备的,协会在备案提交之日起5个工作日内一次性告知报备义务人补正。按照要求补正的,协会在材料齐备后5个工作日内出具电子备案确认函。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 622,
      "end_char": 728,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00020",
      "text": "第三章 自律管理",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 730,
      "end_char": 738,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00021",
      "text": "第十一条 报备义务人应当真实、准确、完整、及时地报送备案材料,并对备案材料内容的合规性负责。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 740,
      "end_char": 786,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00022",
      "text": "第十二条 协会与上海证券交易所、深圳证券交易所建立沟通衔接机制和备案数据共享机制。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 788,
      "end_char": 829,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00023",
      "text": "第十三条 协会会员类报备义务人及其相关业务人员违反本指引的,协会根据《中国证券业协会自律管理措施和纪律处分实施办法》采取相应自律惩戒措施,并计入协会诚信信息管理系统;涉嫌违法违规的,由协会报告中国证监会及其他有权机构。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 831,
      "end_char": 940,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00024",
      "text": "非协会会员的报备义务人及其相关业务人员违反本指引或涉嫌违法违规的,由协会报告中国证监会及其他有权机构。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 942,
      "end_char": 993,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00025",
      "text": "第四章 附 则",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 995,
      "end_char": 1002,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00026",
      "text": "第十四条 信用保护合约主协议及补充协议在协会备案,不代表协会合规性审查,不构成市场准入,也不豁免相关主体的违规责任。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 1004,
      "end_char": 1062,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00027",
      "text": "第十五条 本指引由协会负责解释。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 1064,
      "end_char": 1080,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00028",
      "text": "第十六条 本指引自发布之日起施行。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body",
      "source_page_end": 0,
      "start_char": 1082,
      "end_char": 1099,
      "table_data": {},
      "formula_data": {},
      "parsing_warnings": [],
      "layout": {}
    }
  ]
}
